            <span class="logo-text">CAE</span>
            <div class="logo-strike"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cae-content">
        <p class="hero-subtitle-text">El servicio de excepción del CAE es una solución legal que te permite liberarte de una deuda injusta.</p>
        
        <div class="cae-benefits">
            <div class="benefit-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <span class="icon-text">✓</span>
                    <div class="icon-pulse"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h3>Análisis de caso gratuito</h3>
                    <p>Evaluamos tu situación particular sin costo y te ofrecemos opciones personalizadas para tu caso.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <span class="icon-text">✓</span>
                    <div class="icon-pulse"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h3>Respaldo jurídico completo</h3>
                    <p>Nuestro equipo de abogados especializados te acompaña durante todo el proceso legal, desde la presentación de la demanda hasta su resolución.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <span class="icon-text">✓</span>
                    <div class="icon-pulse"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h3>Pago justo y transparente</h3>
                    <p>Solo pagas cuando obtenemos resultados. Sin costos ocultos ni tarifas iniciales que compliquen tu situación financiera.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <span class="icon-text">✓</span>
                    <div class="icon-pulse"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h3>Atención personalizada</h3>
                    <p>Te asignamos un asesor dedicado que te mantendrá informado sobre el avance de tu caso y responderá todas tus consultas durante el proceso.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .cae-description-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 3rem 0;
        color: var(--color-dark);
        background: transparent;
        box-shadow: none;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .cae-description-container {
            display: block;
        }
    }
    
    .cae-logo-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-width: 300px;
    }
    
    .cae-logo {
        position: relative;
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #e0e0e0);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        border: 3px solid white;
    }
    
.cae-titulo {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-red) !important;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
}
    .logo-text {
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--color-red);
        letter-spacing: -2px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }


    
    .logo-strike {
        position: absolute;
        width: 150%;
        height: 6px;
        background-color: var(--color-red);
        transform: rotate(-45deg);
        animation: strikeThrough 1.5s ease-out forwards;
        transform-origin: center center;
    }
    
    @keyframes strikeThrough {
        0% { width: 0; opacity: 0; }
        50% { opacity: 1; }
        100% { width: 150%; opacity: 1; }
    }
    
    .cae-content {
        flex: 1;
    }
    
    .hero-subtitle-text {
        font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--color-dark);
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    
    .cae-intro {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #555;
    }
    
    .cae-benefits {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        width: 100%;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .cae-benefits {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        }
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 1200px) {
        .cae-benefits {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        }
    }
    
    .benefit-item {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.9) 0%, rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.9) 100%);
        padding: 1.8rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
    
    .benefit-item::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.05) 0%, rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.02) 100%);
        transition: height 0.5s ease;
        z-index: 0;
    }
    
    .benefit-item:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        border-color: rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.2);
    }
    
    .benefit-item:hover::before {
        height: 100%;
    }
    
    .benefit-icon {
        background-color: var(--color-red);
        color: white;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        position: relative;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.3);
        z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .icon-text {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 3;
    }
    
    .icon-pulse {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: var(--color-red);
        opacity: 0.8;
        animation: iconPulse 2s infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes iconPulse {
        0% {
            transform: scale(1);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        50% {
            transform: scale(1.2);
            opacity: 0;
        }
        100% {
            transform: scale(1);
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    
    .benefit-text {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .benefit-text h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
        color: var(--color-red);
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .benefit-text h3::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background-color: var(--color-red);
        transition: width 0.5s ease;
    }
    
    .benefit-item:hover .benefit-text h3::after {
        width: 50px;
    }
    
    .benefit-text p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-dark);
        line-height: 1.6;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .benefit-item:hover .benefit-text h3 {
        transform: translateX(5px);
    }
    
    .benefit-item:hover .benefit-text p {
        color: #000;
    }
    
    .cae-process {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.9) 0%, rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.9) 100%);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    
    .cae-process h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-red);
    }
    
    .process-steps {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin: 0;
    }
    
    .process-steps li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .cae-guarantee {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.9) 0%, rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.9) 100%);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        border-left: 4px solid var(--color-red);
    }
    
    .cae-guarantee h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--color-red);
    }
    
    .cae-guarantee p {
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--color-dark);
    }
    
    .cae-cta {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .cae-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: var(--color-red);
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.3);
    }
    
    .cae-button:hover {
        background-color: var(--color-red-bright);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.4);
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .cae-logo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
    }
    
    .title-style {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
        line-height: 1.2;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: var(--color-red);
    }
    
    .title-line {
        display: block;
        animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }
    
    .title-line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .title-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    
    @keyframes slideInLeft {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-50px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInBenefit {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    
    .benefit-item:nth-child(1) {
        animation: fadeInBenefit 0.6s ease-out 0.1s forwards;
        opacity: 0;
    }
    
    .benefit-item:nth-child(2) {
        animation: fadeInBenefit 0.6s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
        opacity: 0;
    }
    
    .benefit-item:nth-child(3) {
        animation: fadeInBenefit 0.6s ease-out 0.5s forwards;
        opacity: 0;
    }
    
    .benefit-item:nth-child(4) {
        animation: fadeInBenefit 0.6s ease-out 0.7s forwards;
        opacity: 0;
    }
</style>